# pm-ai-agents .gitignore
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file tells git which files to NEVER commit to the public repo.
# The key rule: anything with real secrets, personal data, or runtime
# artefacts belongs here.

# ── API Keys & Secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NEVER commit the real .env file. Use .env.example instead.
.env
*.env
!.env.example

# ── Personal Voice & Style Files ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# MY_STYLE.md and my_posts.md contain your real LinkedIn writing style
# and personal post examples. Keep them local; share the .example versions.
MY_STYLE.md
my_posts.md

# ── Generated Outputs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The output/ folder contains your actual generated LinkedIn posts and
# posting history. This is personal content — not for public sharing.
# See samples/ for curated before/after examples instead.
output/

# ── Eval Results ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Run-specific eval results are noisy and machine-specific.
**/evals/results/

# ── Python Artefacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# ── macOS System Files ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# ── IDE & Editor Files ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
